ColourMenu_GetColour
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<ColourMenu=>colourmenu/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	ColourMenu_GetColour
Veneer:	<colourmenu_get_colour>
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = ColourMenu object ID
r2 = 1
{f}
#indent

On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = Wimp Colour
      0-15 - Colours
      16   - None
     -1    - Nothing Selected
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the selected colour.